{"tid":1554783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉拆除針對區議員鄺葆賢橫額　22歲青年被控盜竊准保釋","createTime":"2019-09-09T06:07:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T06:24:56.000Z","uid":53379,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d20918d1126d49969c433d88090c8883a6cb1cf6","tid":1554783,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:07:37.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">涉拆除針對區議員鄺葆賢橫額　22歲青年被控盜竊准保釋</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n紅磡出現針對急症室醫生兼區議員鄺葆賢的橫額，一名22歲青年上周五（6日）晚涉嫌將之拆除並棄於垃圾桶，被巡警發現即場拘捕。青年被控一項盜竊罪，今日（9日）提堂，暫毋須答辯，獲保釋至10月21日再應訊。據了解，涉案橫額印有「鄺葆賢最懶，區議會大會四年零文件」字眼。<br />\n<br />\n被告林嘉淇報稱任職通信技術系統維修員，他被控於今年9月6日在紅磡機利士南路6號外馬路中心偷竊一塊黃色橫額，而該橫額為一名不知名人士的財產。<br />\n<br />\n辯方申請將案件押後，以待索取控方文件。裁判官批准申請，將案件押後至10月21日再訊，被告獲保釋外出，須繳交500元金保釋金，其間不得離開香港，住在報稱地址，以及每週到警署報到一次。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，案發當晚約10時，被告用鉗剪除一幅掛在路邊約240厘米乘以90厘米大、黃底黑字的橫額，並將其扔入垃圾桶，巡邏警員見狀隨即拘捕被告，惟至今仍未知橫額的物主是誰。<br />\n<br />\n涉案橫額內容針對前青年新政、現任九龍城區議會黃埔西選區議員鄺葆賢，上面印有「鄺葆賢最懶，區議會大會四年零文件」字樣。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190909/s00001/1568002259215/%e6%b6%89%e6%8b%86%e9%99%a4%e9%87%9d%e5%b0%8d%e5%8d%80%e8%ad%b0%e5%93%a1%e9%84%ba%e8%91%86%e8%b3%a2%e6%a9%ab%e9%a1%8d-22%e6%ad%b2%e9%9d%92%e5%b9%b4%e8%a2%ab%e6%8e%a7%e7%9b%9c%e7%ab%8a%e5%87%86%e4%bf%9d%e9%87%8b\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190909%2Fs00001%2F1568002259215%2F%25e6%25b6%2589%25e6%258b%2586%25e9%2599%25a4%25e9%2587%259d%25e5%25b0%258d%25e5%258d%2580%25e8%25ad%25b0%25e5%2593%25a1%25e9%2584%25ba%25e8%2591%2586%25e8%25b3%25a2%25e6%25a9%25ab%25e9%25a1%258d-22%25e6%25ad%25b2%25e9%259d%2592%25e5%25b9%25b4%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e6%258e%25a7%25e7%259b%259c%25e7%25ab%258a%25e5%2587%2586%25e4%25bf%259d%25e9%2587%258b&d=uCl2s%2BJteilWOEmp%2BZl8kQomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=437e3451\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190909%2Fs00001%2F1568002259215%2F%25e6%25b6%2589%25e6%258b%2586%25e9%2599%25a4%25e9%2587%259d%25e5%25b0%258d%25e5%258d%2580%25e8%25ad%25b0%25e5%2593%25a1%25e9%2584%25ba%25e8%2591%2586%25e8%25b3%25a2%25e6%25a9%25ab%25e9%25a1%258d-22%25e6%25ad%25b2%25e9%259d%2592%25e5%25b9%25b4%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e6%258e%25a7%25e7%259b%259c%25e7%25ab%258a%25e5%2587%2586%25e4%25bf%259d%25e9%2587%258b&h=1dd3c282\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190909/s00001/1568002259215/%e6%b6%89%e6%8b%86%e9%99%a4%e9%87%9d%e5%b0%8d%e5%8d%80%e8%ad%b0%e5%93%a1%e9%84%ba%e8%91%86%e8%b3%a2%e6%a9%ab%e9%a1%8d-22%e6%ad%b2%e9%9d%92%e5%b9%b4%e8%a2%ab%e6%8e%a7%e7%9b%9c%e7%ab%8a%e5%87%86%e4%bf%9d%e9%87%8b</a><br />\n<br />\n選擇性執法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70581f16f526b849dc2883dd4af98966095f0947","tid":1554783,"uid":66324,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:08:40.000Z","msg":"撕連儂牆果D又唔見佢地拉?"},{"pid":"80810bf66e0c2bc0bee2d798dcb81faa98833b39","tid":1554783,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70581f16f526b849dc2883dd4af98966095f0947","tid":1554783,"uid":66324,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:08:40.000Z","msg":"撕連儂牆果D又唔見佢地拉?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:14:39.000Z","msg":"仲會保護佢哋"},{"pid":"a94c6604f98c32c0b033c4deef22f2fe929d1500","tid":1554783,"uid":35930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:15:50.000Z","msg":"偷黎打飛機？"},{"pid":"eec8246148a4a19a77686a1ff6c4bcb641a89d2a","tid":1554783,"uid":8880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:16:06.000Z","msg":"即係撕連儂牆係盜竊罪?"},{"pid":"55260d667817e47bd525467e3a503f6e7e990f1a","tid":1554783,"uid":103230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:16:34.000Z","msg":"個橫額都冇人認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n